Package: AddiVortes
Title: (Bayesian) Additive Voronoi Tessellations
Version: 0.1.15
Date: 2025-07-15
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Adam", "Stone", , "adam.stone2@durham.ac.uk",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-0058-6117")),
      person("John Paul", "Gosling", , "john-paul.gosling@durham.ac.uk",
             role = c("aut"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4072-3022")))
Description: Implements the Bayesian Additive Voronoi Tessellation (AddiVortes) 
    model for non-parametric regression and classification. This package allows 
    users to fit the model estimate posterior distributions and visualise the 
    resulting tessellations. It is particularly useful for spatial data analysis 
    and complex function approximation where the underlying structure is unknown.
